{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Build a complete, fully customizable Shopify Liquid section called "Haramoon Science Three Column" that matches this exact layout: a bold full-width colored banner with a large centered headline, a subtitle underneath it, and below that a white card containing three equal columns separated by vertical dividers.
    
    HEADER AREA:
    
    Full-width background (color picker setting)
    Large bold centered headline — default text: "The Science Behind HARAMOON"
    Smaller italic or light-weight centered subtitle below — default text: "Understanding the K-Beauty Difference Compared to Western Formulas"
    All text colors customizable via color pickers
    Padding top/bottom on the header area: range slider settings
    THREE COLUMN CARD:
    
    White background card with rounded corners and subtle shadow sitting below the header (overlapping slightly if possible, like a floating card)
    Three equal-width columns separated by thin vertical divider lines
    Each column has:
    A small all-caps label at the top (e.g. "THE PROBLEM") — customizable text, color, font size
    A horizontal rule/divider line below the label
    A bold larger heading below the divider (e.g. "Weak Barrier") — customizable text and color
    A paragraph of body text below (e.g. "Compromised skin barrier leads to moisture loss, sensitivity, and visible signs of aging.") — customizable text and color
    DEFAULT TEXT FOR THE THREE COLUMNS:
    
    Column 1: Label = "THE PROBLEM" | Heading = "Weak Barrier" | Body = "Compromised skin barrier leads to moisture loss, sensitivity, and visible signs of aging."
    Column 2: Label = "THE SCIENCE" | Heading = "HARAMOON's Proprietary Approach" | Body = "HARAMOON's proprietary K-Beauty ingredients rebuild the skin's protective barrier, restore lipid balance, and signal deep cellular repair — without the harsh actives found in Western formulas."
    Column 3: Label = "THE RESULT" | Heading = "Glass Skin" | Body = "Plump, luminous, resilient skin with improved texture and long-lasting hydration."
    SECTION SETTINGS (every value must be editable in the theme editor sidebar):
    
    Header background color picker
    Header headline text (single line text input)
    Header headline color picker
    Header headline font size (range: 20–60px, default 36)
    Header subtitle text (single line text input)
    Header subtitle color picker
    Header subtitle font size (range: 12–28px, default 16)
    Header padding top (range: 0–120px, step 4, default 48)
    Header padding bottom (range: 0–120px, step 4, default 48)
    Card background color picker (default white)
    Card border radius (range: 0–30px, default 12)
    Card padding inside (range: 0–80px, step 4, default 40)
    Card margin top (range: -60 to 0px — to allow floating overlap effect, default -32)
    Divider line color picker (default light gray)
    Column label color picker
    Column label font size (range: 8–16px, default 11)
    Column heading color picker
    Column heading font size (range: 14–36px, default 22)
    Column body text color picker
    Column body font size (range: 12–20px, default 15)
    Section max-width (range: 800–1400px, default 1200)
    Section outer padding left/right (range: 0–80px, default 24)
    FOR EACH OF THE THREE COLUMNS, expose these as individual settings (Column 1, Column 2, Column 3 — use setting id prefixes like col1_label, col1_heading, col1_body, col2_label, etc.):
    
    Label text
    Heading text
    Body text
    RESPONSIVE BEHAVIOR:
    
    On desktop: three columns side by side with vertical dividers between them
    On tablet (max-width 900px): two columns
    On mobile (max-width 600px): single column stacked, dividers become horizontal rules
    OUTPUT: A complete working .liquid section file with all HTML, CSS (scoped with the section id), and a valid {% schema %} block at the bottom. Do not use placeholder comments — write every line of actual working code.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = section.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .haramoon-science-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .haramoon-science-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ section.settings.header_bg_color }};
    padding-top: {{ section.settings.header_padding_top }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.header_padding_bottom }}px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .haramoon-science-header-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ section.settings.section_max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-left: {{ section.settings.section_outer_padding }}px;
    padding-right: {{ section.settings.section_outer_padding }}px;
  }

  .haramoon-science-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ section.settings.headline_color }};
    font-size: {{ section.settings.headline_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .haramoon-science-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ section.settings.subtitle_color }};
    font-size: {{ section.settings.subtitle_font_size }}px;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .haramoon-science-card-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ section.settings.section_max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-left: {{ section.settings.section_outer_padding }}px;
    padding-right: {{ section.settings.section_outer_padding }}px;
    margin-top: {{ section.settings.card_margin_top }}px;
  }

  .haramoon-science-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ section.settings.card_bg_color }};
    border-radius: {{ section.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    padding: {{ section.settings.card_padding }}px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1px 1fr 1px 1fr;
    gap: {{ section.settings.card_padding }}px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .haramoon-science-divider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 1px;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: {{ section.settings.divider_color }};
    align-self: stretch;
  }

  .haramoon-science-column-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .haramoon-science-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ section.settings.label_color }};
    font-size: {{ section.settings.label_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .haramoon-science-label-divider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background-color: {{ section.settings.divider_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .haramoon-science-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ section.settings.heading_color }};
    font-size: {{ section.settings.heading_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .haramoon-science-body-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ section.settings.body_color }};
    font-size: {{ section.settings.body_font_size }}px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 900px) {
    .haramoon-science-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1px 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto auto;
    }

    .haramoon-science-column-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(1) {
      grid-column: 1;
      grid-row: 1;
    }

    .haramoon-science-divider-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(2) {
      grid-column: 2;
      grid-row: 1;
    }

    .haramoon-science-column-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(3) {
      grid-column: 3;
      grid-row: 1;
    }

    .haramoon-science-divider-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(4) {
      display: none;
    }

    .haramoon-science-column-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(5) {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      grid-row: 2;
      padding-top: {{ section.settings.card_padding }}px;
      border-top: 1px solid {{ section.settings.divider_color }};
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
    .haramoon-science-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto;
      gap: {{ section.settings.card_padding }}px;
    }

    .haramoon-science-column-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-column: 1;
      padding-top: 0;
      border-top: none;
    }

    .haramoon-science-column-{{ ai_gen_id }}:not(:first-child) {
      padding-top: {{ section.settings.card_padding }}px;
      border-top: 1px solid {{ section.settings.divider_color }};
    }

    .haramoon-science-divider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      display: none;
    }

    .haramoon-science-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ section.settings.headline_font_size }}px * 0.7);
    }

    .haramoon-science-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: calc({{ section.settings.subtitle_font_size }}px * 0.9);
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="haramoon-science-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
  <div class="haramoon-science-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="haramoon-science-header-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if section.settings.headline != blank %}
        <h2 class="haramoon-science-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ section.settings.headline }}</h2>
      {% endif %}
      {% if section.settings.subtitle != blank %}
        <p class="haramoon-science-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ section.settings.subtitle }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="haramoon-science-card-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="haramoon-science-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="haramoon-science-column-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if section.settings.col1_label != blank %}
          <p class="haramoon-science-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ section.settings.col1_label }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <hr class="haramoon-science-label-divider-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if section.settings.col1_heading != blank %}
          <h3 class="haramoon-science-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ section.settings.col1_heading }}</h3>
        {% endif %}
        {% if section.settings.col1_body != blank %}
          <p class="haramoon-science-body-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ section.settings.col1_body }}</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="haramoon-science-divider-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>

      <div class="haramoon-science-column-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if section.settings.col2_label != blank %}
          <p class="haramoon-science-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ section.settings.col2_label }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <hr class="haramoon-science-label-divider-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if section.settings.col2_heading != blank %}
          <h3 class="haramoon-science-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ section.settings.col2_heading }}</h3>
        {% endif %}
        {% if section.settings.col2_body != blank %}
          <p class="haramoon-science-body-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ section.settings.col2_body }}</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>

      <div class="haramoon-science-divider-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>

      <div class="haramoon-science-column-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if section.settings.col3_label != blank %}
          <p class="haramoon-science-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ section.settings.col3_label }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <hr class="haramoon-science-label-divider-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if section.settings.col3_heading != blank %}
          <h3 class="haramoon-science-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ section.settings.col3_heading }}</h3>
        {% endif %}
        {% if section.settings.col3_body != blank %}
          <p class="haramoon-science-body-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ section.settings.col3_body }}</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

